posting_body: ['Larson Apartments', '3706 Larson Lane W, University Place, WA, 98466', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 83', 'OR Text', '83', 'to', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', 'Welcome to Larson at University Place!', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 596 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Experience the best that University Place and the South Sound have to offer.', 'Boasting a variety of floor plans ranging from thoughtfully designed Studios to amazing Two-Bedrooms, all featuring indulgent finishes and high-end appliances.', 'Larson residents are able to perfectly balance work and play with planned amenities like a private fitness studio and reservable office space in addition to our roof-top retreat and pet spa; there is something for everyone!', "Minutes from all your favorite shopping and abundant recreational opportunities, you have a can't miss combination of style and convenience at Larson!", 'Pet Policy', 'Dogs and cats allowed.', 'Pet Limit- 2 Weight limit-', '70 lbs', 'One time Fee- $600 2nd Pet-', 'additional $300 fee', 'Monthly pet rent- $45 per pet', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 8:30AM-5:30PM', 'LALLe711I']
